PrecisEnactment of an ORDER AMENDING THE SCHEDULE TO THE CUSTOMS TARIFF, 2002-2 - which eliminates tariffs on certain electric motors, maintains the duty- free tariff on certain woven upholstery fabrics and clarifies and expands the scope of the duty-free tariff on certain cotton fabrics used to make tailored shirts.
